short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Choose the best gate, pass through it, bring stickman warriors together to clash with the opposing crowd. Become the crowd master!
short.zh_CN: 选择最好的门，穿过它，将火柴人战士们聚集起来，与对方人群展开冲突。成为人群的主宰，带领你的队伍穿越拥挤的城市，直到这场史诗般的比赛结束。
